  "title": "HR Internship Summer 2026 #HFQ",
  "description": "<p>Responsibilities:</p><p>•⁠  ⁠Identify and assess potential candidates</p><p>•⁠  ⁠Conduct interview and manage selection procedures</p><p>•⁠  ⁠Design job descriptions and interview questions</p><p>•⁠  ⁠Organize and attend recruitment events</p><p>•⁠  ⁠Lead discussions in quarterly and annual hiring needs by department</p><p>•⁠  ⁠Foster long-term relationships with past applicants and potential candidates</p><p>•⁠  ⁠Involve actively in Human Resource activities with regards to Hiring and Managing of potential candidates<br /></p><p>Requirements:</p><p>•⁠  ⁠Degree in any Discipline</p><p>•⁠  ⁠Candidates with strong track record in sports or co-curricular activities will have an added advantage</p><p>•⁠  ⁠Candidate with great team spirit, persistency, good communication and interpersonal skills are welcome to apply</p><p></p><p>Interested candidates please send in your resume to:</p><p>valerie@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p></p><p>EA Personnel: Valerie Yong Kian Fung</p><p>CEI No.: R1103704</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd, EA License No.: 99C4599</p>",
